MessagePack PHP extension
-----------
Binary-based efficient data interchange format.


*Requirements

  MessagePack PHP Extension is only tested on Linux , but it may run on other
  UNIX-like platforms.

  gcc >= 4.1
  php5-dev >= 5.2

   are required to build.


*Installation

    $ phpize
    $ ./configure
    $ make
    $ sudo make install

  To load extension, copy ini/msgpack.ini to included path and restart apache.

  For example, to install on Debian GNU/Linux, 
    $ cp ini/msgpack.ini /etc/php5/apache2/conf.d/
    $ sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 restart

*Test

  phpunit is required to test.
    $ cd test
    $ make test

*Usage

    see example/sample.php for example.

    $  php sample.php



